Due to the epidemic, many graduates failed to appreciate the sense of ceremony of dialing ears and awarding degree certificates on the spot, so they transferred the sense of ceremony online.
The data showed that the live popularity of the 2.5-hour song party peaked at more than 35 million.
"Follow your heart, seize the opportunity and do not care about the consequences. Sometimes, there will be unexpected gains."
