According to a recent report in Russia's Yediot, Wuzhika-52M is called "Super Alligator". Its development contract was signed by the Russian military and military industrial units in April last year. At present, the first two upgraded Wuzhi are being transformed and replaced at the Far East Helicopter Manufacturing Plant of the Russian "Progress" Aerospace Group Corporation. Its state-level testing and improvement finishing work will be completed by October 2022.
