In addition, the employing unit shall provide full-time and part-time health managers and organize and carry out employee health check-ups on a regular basis.
In terms of the physical and mental health of minors, the consultation draft proposes that the sale of alcoholic beverages to minors is prohibited, while the location of the sale of alcoholic beverages is restricted. Those who violate the regulations will be ordered by the market supervision and administration department to make corrections and fined 30,000 yuan.
In addition to the "prohibition of alcohol", minors should also "exercise more".
According to the requirements of the consultation draft, the school should arrange more than one hour of physical activity for students every day.
For online games, the departments of public security, culture, radio, television, tourism and sports, network supervision, health and health shall improve the health supervision system of Internet Internet service business premises, establish a health review system for online games, and create a good communication space and communication culture for promoting the healthy growth of young people.
In addition, the consultation draft also proposed that influenza patients must wear masks when entering and leaving public places, and that medical and health institutions should be fined 20,000 yuan for divulging patients' privacy without consent.
